    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras/aadb45f5e5b47c571a3c9bc44107523f.poster.avif?t=1752280896\" width=600 height=672 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras/aadb45f5e5b47c571a3c9bc44107523f.webm?t=1752280896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras/aadb45f5e5b47c571a3c9bc44107523f.mp4?t=1752280896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将经典Breakout带入现代的终极进化版</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用连击冲击高分！由于每次方块的排列都不同，每一局都充满新鲜感，让人百玩不厌的Breakout闪亮登场。本作拥有关卡选择和9段评价系统等丰富内容，游戏体验满点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras/d648863c0b918bdef1077f212de49e88.avif?t=1752280896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras_big/d648863c0b918bdef1077f212de49e88.avif?t=1752280896 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>连击系统</strong>：连续击破方块可大幅提升得分！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随机排列</strong>：方块排列每次都会变化，拥有超过3万种组合！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关卡选择</strong>：可自由选择挑战喜爱的关卡（第1至第10关）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>评分系统</strong>：根据得分与进度进行9段评价，从S+到E。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精美画面</strong>：再现80年代街机风格，酷炫华丽的视觉效果令人目不暇接。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏结束条件</strong>：失误5次即游戏结束，紧张刺激感拉满！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras/a4539043a7b72bf3fb29d9ec3d4641d4.avif?t=1752280896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras_big/a4539043a7b72bf3fb29d9ec3d4641d4.avif?t=1752280896 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2025年5月，重大更新震撼登场！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过本次更新，本作跃升为全新境界的Breakout。<br>程序从零重新构建，画面大幅升级，并新增连击系统，大大提升了挑战高分的乐趣！<br>在传承经典精神的同时，也让现代玩家为之惊艳。<br>请尽情享受这款酷炫而充满情感的Breakout体验。<br>※更新时请先卸载旧版本，再重新安装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras/2802824efaa7e26b20e9af0a6d5fe9cd.avif?t=1752280896\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182910/extras_big/2802824efaa7e26b20e9af0a6d5fe9cd.avif?t=1752280896 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >向70年代致敬</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我制作这款游戏，是出于对70年代雅达利公司《Breakout》的深厚情感。<br>那个年代，甚至连“电视游戏”这个概念都还不存在，而我却深深被这款游戏震撼至今。<br>那种简单却令人沉迷的玩法、逐步逼近的方块、考验反应神经的紧张感——<br>我想要再次重温当年的感动，于是创作了这部作品。<br>Breakout穿越50年时光重生，欢迎你来挑战！</p>",
